DATA NOTICE

The legal texts served by this software are sourced from Fedlex
(https://fedlex.data.admin.ch), the official publication platform of the
Swiss Federal Chancellery. That data is published as open government data
under the terms described at https://www.fedlex.admin.ch/en/utility/legal-information.

THIS SOFTWARE IS NOT A SUBSTITUTE FOR LEGAL ADVICE. The data is provided for
informational purposes only. While the software retrieves data directly from
official Swiss government sources, no guarantee is made regarding the accuracy,
completeness, or timeliness of the information. Always refer to the official
Fedlex platform (https://www.fedlex.admin.ch) or consult a qualified legal
professional for authoritative legal information.
